The paper proposes a semantic search framework for RDF data utilizing keyword-based searches and near neighbor explorations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Database (cs.DB) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of entity type semantics and relevance confidence scores indicate a focus on Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Semantic Web (cs.SI) technologies. The evaluation of the framework's effectiveness and accuracy also suggests a possible connection to Machine Learning (cs.LG).
